snippet.textDisplay: I've seen every Christopher Nolan movie up to this point , and each one is a masterpiece .  I am used to Christopher's style when it comes to movies , but something here , in this trailer seems  off . Yes , his movies come with a twist , a : ,, WTF !! '' moment , or 10 . But after watching the trailer , and after feeling the vibe that is sends , TENET , will be something else . And what I mean by that is : THIS MOVIE SCARES ME . SCARES THE SHIT OUT OF ME . I feel like I will witness a tragedy live , a really messed up one too . There will be no way out of it because of how beatifully is it  presented , but the scars will be deep . A real psychological horror which will make me say after watching it : I've never loved and feared a movie that much in my life .
